# Light-Pong

This is the classic game of pong, rebuilt for lidar sensors and moving heads.

The position of the players are controlled by the position of the players, the ball is a ball of light.

The players have to position within a zone of a certain side on their side of the playing field.


## Installation and Setup
setup by installing the requirements in a new python virtual environment
``` bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

set the ip address and the port of the light controller using the variables in the beginning of the pong.py


start the game with `python pong.py`